  Victoria captioned the adorable Instagram snap: “Sunday swim with my little water baby! Kisses #HarperSeven.” The candid picture showed the mum and daughter letting their hair down while posing for the camera as they enjoyed some time in the pool Victoria pulled a silly face for the camera, as she showed off her au-naturel beauty with a minimal makeup look. Only the black straps of her swimsuit were visible, while she opted to wear her hair in a messy bun. Harper’s hair matched her mum’s as she beamed alongside her in bright yellow.  